                "text": "trailofbits.python.tarfile-extractall-traversal.tarfile-extractall-traversal"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Possible path traversal through `tarfile.open($PATH).extractall()` if the source tar is controlled by an attacker"
              },
              "help": {
